From b4dd7640d0d95f975a6ab8782145f2b59a2aba68 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Samy <samycloutier30@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 15 Apr 2026 02:42:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(trending-card): always resolve clip URL via GQL, remove
 thumbnailToVideoUrl

Root cause: thumbnailToVideoUrl() derived MP4 URLs from thumbnail URL patterns
and could silently return a URL for the wrong clip. Fix: always fetch the signed
URL via /api/clips/video-url (Twitch GQL persisted query). Added reset effect so
cached URLs clear when clip.id or clip.external_url changes.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
